<item>
            <title>[HIVE-9567] JSON SerDe not escaping special chars when writing char/varchar data</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-9567</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When writing string data to fields designated as char/varchar fields, JsonSerDe does not escape special characters, which can invalidate the JSON.&lt;br/&gt;
Looks like string columns use SerDeUtils.escapeString() when building the JSON string. Char/varchar need to do the same.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
